snippet.title: Super Indie Karts x Teslagrad Crossover
snippet.description:
Here Comes A New RaceTrack!! - It's Tesla Tower from Teslagrad!

Super Indie Karts is a '90s style kart racer available in Early Access on Steam (for Windows and Mac) and OUYA featuring racetrack and kart crossovers with a heap of super Indie Games. http://store.steampowered.com/app/323670/

Teslagrad is a stunningly beautiful platformer with magnetism and the harnessing of electricity weaved into it's game mechanics. Available for PlayStation3&4, WiiU, and Steam (for Windows, Mac and Linux), you can find more info at http://teslagrad.com
